{
  "video_id": "KaiwGb0csas",
  "title": "When performing gets in the way of improving | Eduardo Briceño | TEDxManhattanBeach",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15569.0,
      "end_time": 19609.0,
      "text": "Most of us go through life trying to do our best at whatever we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19609.0,
      "end_time": 22209.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s our job, family, schoolb"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22209.0,
      "end_time": 24049.0,
      "text": "or anything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24049.0,
      "end_time": 26729.0,
      "text": "I feel that way. I try my best."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26729.0,
      "end_time": 29649.0,
      "text": "But some time ago, I came to a realization"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29649.0,
      "end_time": 33449.0,
      "text": "that I wasn&#39;t getting much better at the things I cared most about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33449.0,
      "end_time": 36649.0,
      "text": "whether it was being a husband or a friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36649.0,
      "end_time": 38889.0,
      "text": "or a professional or teammate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38889.0,
      "end_time": 40929.0,
      "text": "and I wasn&#39;t improving much at those things"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40929.0,
      "end_time": 43489.0,
      "text": "even though I was spending a lot of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43489.0,
      "end_time": 46009.0,
      "text": "working hard at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46009.0,
      "end_time": 49409.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve since realized from conversations I&#39;ve had and from research"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49409.0,
      "end_time": 52089.0,
      "text": "that this stagnation, despite hard work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52089.0,
      "end_time": 53849.0,
      "text": "turns out to be pretty common."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53849.0,
      "end_time": 56729.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to share with you some insights into why that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56729.0,
      "end_time": 58969.0,
      "text": "and what we can all do about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58969.0,
      "end_time": 61489.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;ve learned is that the most effective people"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61489.0,
      "end_time": 63489.0,
      "text": "and teams in any domain"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63489.0,
      "end_time": 65809.0,
      "text": "do something we can all emulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65809.0,
      "end_time": 69889.0,
      "text": "They go through life deliberately alternating between two zones:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69889.0,
      "end_time": 72969.0,
      "text": "the learning zone and the performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72969.0,
      "end_time": 75649.0,
      "text": "The learning zone is when our goal is to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75649.0,
      "end_time": 78769.0,
      "text": "Then we do activities designed for improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78769.0,
      "end_time": 81249.0,
      "text": "concentrating on what we haven&#39;t mastered yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81249.0,
      "end_time": 83729.0,
      "text": "which means we have to expect to make mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83729.0,
      "end_time": 85969.0,
      "text": "knowing that we will learn from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85969.0,
      "end_time": 89729.0,
      "text": "That is very different from what we do when we&#39;re in our performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89729.0,
      "end_time": 94049.0,
      "text": "which is when our goal is to do something as best as we can, to execute."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94049.0,
      "end_time": 96689.0,
      "text": "Then we concentrate on what we have already mastered"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96689.0,
      "end_time": 99649.0,
      "text": "and we try to minimize mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99649.0,
      "end_time": 102089.0,
      "text": "Both of these zones should be part of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102089.0,
      "end_time": 105369.0,
      "text": "but being clear about when we want to be in each of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105369.0,
      "end_time": 107689.0,
      "text": "with what goal, focus and expectations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107689.0,
      "end_time": 110529.0,
      "text": "helps us better perform and better improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110529.0,
      "end_time": 113489.0,
      "text": "The performance zone maximizes our immediate performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113489.0,
      "end_time": 115609.0,
      "text": "while the learning zone maximizes our growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115609.0,
      "end_time": 118129.0,
      "text": "and our future performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118129.0,
      "end_time": 120209.0,
      "text": "The reason many of us don&#39;t improve much"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120209.0,
      "end_time": 121969.0,
      "text": "despite our hard work"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121969.0,
      "end_time": 126689.0,
      "text": "is that we tend to spend almost all of our time in the performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126689.0,
      "end_time": 128089.0,
      "text": "This hinders our growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128089.0,
      "end_time": 132849.0,
      "text": "and ironically, over the long term, also our performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132849.0,
      "end_time": 135569.0,
      "text": "So what does the learning zone look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135569.0,
      "end_time": 137609.0,
      "text": "Take Demosthenes, a political leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137609.0,
      "end_time": 141049.0,
      "text": "and the greatest orator and lawyer in ancient Greece."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141049.0,
      "end_time": 144728.0,
      "text": "To become great, he didn&#39;t spend all his time"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 144728.0,
      "end_time": 147169.0,
      "text": "just being an orator or a lawyer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147169.0,
      "end_time": 149369.0,
      "text": "which would be his performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149369.0,
      "end_time": 152409.0,
      "text": "But instead, he did activities designed for improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152409.0,
      "end_time": 153809.0,
      "text": "Of course, he studied a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153809.0,
      "end_time": 156649.0,
      "text": "He studied law and philosophy with guidance from mentors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156649.0,
      "end_time": 161209.0,
      "text": "but he also realized that being a lawyer involved persuading other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 161209.0,
      "end_time": 163609.0,
      "text": "so he also studied great speeches"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 163609.0,
      "end_time": 165449.0,
      "text": "and acting."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165449.0,
      "end_time": 169769.0,
      "text": "To get rid of an odd habit he had of involuntarily lifting his shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169769.0,
      "end_time": 172209.0,
      "text": "he practiced his speeches in front of a mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 172209.0,
      "end_time": 175209.0,
      "text": "and he suspended a sword from the ceiling"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 175209.0,
      "end_time": 176969.0,
      "text": "so that if he raised his shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176969.0,
      "end_time": 178209.0,
      "text": "it would hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178209.0,
      "end_time": 179849.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179849.0,
      "end_time": 182009.0,
      "text": "To speak more clearly despite a lisp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182009.0,
      "end_time": 185649.0,
      "text": "he went through his speeches with stones in his mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 185649.0,
      "end_time": 187049.0,
      "text": "He built an underground room"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 187049.0,
      "end_time": 189209.0,
      "text": "where he could practice without interruptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189209.0,
      "end_time": 190649.0,
      "text": "and not disturb other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 190649.0,
      "end_time": 192809.0,
      "text": "And since courts at the time were very noisy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 192809.0,
      "end_time": 194689.0,
      "text": "he also practiced by the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194689.0,
      "end_time": 198209.0,
      "text": "projecting his voice above the roar of the waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198209.0,
      "end_time": 199929.0,
      "text": "His activities in the learning zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 199929.0,
      "end_time": 202449.0,
      "text": "were very different from his activities in court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 202449.0,
      "end_time": 204569.0,
      "text": "his performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 204569.0,
      "end_time": 205809.0,
      "text": "In the learning zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 205809.0,
      "end_time": 208609.0,
      "text": "he did what Dr. Anders Ericsson calls deliberate practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208609.0,
      "end_time": 212169.0,
      "text": "This involves breaking down abilities into component skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 212169.0,
      "end_time": 215089.0,
      "text": "being clear about what subskill we&#39;re working to improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215089.0,
      "end_time": 217089.0,
      "text": "like keeping our shoulders down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217089.0,
      "end_time": 219969.0,
      "text": "giving full concentration to a high level of challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 219969.0,
      "end_time": 221409.0,
      "text": "outside our comfort zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 221409.0,
      "end_time": 223769.0,
      "text": "just beyond what we can currently do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223769.0,
      "end_time": 227009.0,
      "text": "using frequent feedback with repetition and adjustments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227009.0,
      "end_time": 230009.0,
      "text": "and ideally engaging the guidance of a skilled coach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230009.0,
      "end_time": 232089.0,
      "text": "because activities designed for improvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 232089.0,
      "end_time": 233369.0,
      "text": "are domain-specific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 233369.0,
      "end_time": 236289.0,
      "text": "and great teachers and coaches know what those activities are"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 236289.0,
      "end_time": 238769.0,
      "text": "and can also give us expert feedback."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 238769.0,
      "end_time": 241489.0,
      "text": "It is this type of practice in the learning zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241489.0,
      "end_time": 243409.0,
      "text": "which leads to substantial improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 243409.0,
      "end_time": 246769.0,
      "text": "not just time on task performing."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 246769.0,
      "end_time": 249969.0,
      "text": "For example, research shows that after the first couple of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249969.0,
      "end_time": 251249.0,
      "text": "working in a profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251249.0,
      "end_time": 253609.0,
      "text": "performance usually plateaus."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 253609.0,
      "end_time": 256689.0,
      "text": "This has been shown to be true in teaching, general medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 256689.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258409.00000000003,
      "text": "nursing and other fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 258409.0,
      "end_time": 262169.0,
      "text": "and it happens because once we think we have become good enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 262169.0,
      "end_time": 263409.0,
      "text": "adequate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 263409.0,
      "end_time": 265689.0,
      "text": "then we stop spending time in the learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 265689.0,
      "end_time": 267889.0,
      "text": "We focus all our time on just doing our job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 267889.0,
      "end_time": 269129.0,
      "text": "performing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269129.0,
      "end_time": 271969.0,
      "text": "which turns out not to be a great way to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271969.0,
      "end_time": 274929.0,
      "text": "But the people who continue to spend time in the learning zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 274929.0,
      "end_time": 277089.0,
      "text": "do continue to always improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277089.0,
      "end_time": 279529.0,
      "text": "The best salespeople at least once a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279529.0,
      "end_time": 282169.0,
      "text": "do activities with the goal of improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 282169.0,
      "end_time": 283969.0,
      "text": "They read to extend their knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283969.0,
      "end_time": 286409.0,
      "text": "consult with colleagues or domain experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 286409.0,
      "end_time": 290169.0,
      "text": "try out new strategies, solicit feedback and reflect."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 290169.0,
      "end_time": 291809.0,
      "text": "The best chess players"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 291809.0,
      "end_time": 295369.0,
      "text": "spend a lot of time not playing games of chess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 295369.0,
      "end_time": 297329.0,
      "text": "which would be their performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 297329.0,
      "end_time": 301729.0,
      "text": "but trying to predict the moves grand masters made and analyzing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 301729.0,
      "end_time": 305849.0,
      "text": "Each of us has probably spent many, many, many hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 305849.0,
      "end_time": 307409.0,
      "text": "typing on a computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 307409.0,
      "end_time": 309009.0,
      "text": "without getting faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 309009.0,
      "end_time": 312449.0,
      "text": "but if we spent 10 to 20 minutes each day"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 312449.0,
      "end_time": 315649.0,
      "text": "fully concentrating on typing 10 to 20 percent faster"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 315649.0,
      "end_time": 317249.0,
      "text": "than our current reliable speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 317249.0,
      "end_time": 318529.0,
      "text": "we would get faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 318529.0,
      "end_time": 321569.0,
      "text": "especially if we also identified what mistakes we&#39;re making"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 321569.0,
      "end_time": 324209.0,
      "text": "and practiced typing those words."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 324209.0,
      "end_time": 327089.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s deliberate practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 327089.0,
      "end_time": 328849.0,
      "text": "In what other parts of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 328849.0,
      "end_time": 330569.0,
      "text": "perhaps that we care more about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 330569.0,
      "end_time": 333129.0,
      "text": "are we working hard but not improving much"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 333129.0,
      "end_time": 337369.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re always in the performance zone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 337369.0,
      "end_time": 340369.0,
      "text": "Now, this is not to say that the performance zone has no value."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 340369.0,
      "end_time": 341609.0,
      "text": "It very much does."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 341609.0,
      "end_time": 344289.0,
      "text": "When I needed a knee surgery, I didn&#39;t tell the surgeon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 344289.0,
      "end_time": 346969.0,
      "text": "&quot;Poke around in there and focus on what you don&#39;t know.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 346969.0,
      "end_time": 348009.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 348009.0,
      "end_time": 350489.0,
      "text": "&quot;We&#39;ll learn from your mistakes!&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 350489.0,
      "end_time": 353769.0,
      "text": "I looked for a surgeon who I felt would do a good job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 353769.0,
      "end_time": 355969.0,
      "text": "and I wanted her to do a good job."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 355969.0,
      "end_time": 357409.0,
      "text": "Being in the performance zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 357409.0,
      "end_time": 360609.0,
      "text": "allows us to get things done as best as we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 360609.0,
      "end_time": 362009.0,
      "text": "It can also be motivating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 362009.0,
      "end_time": 365609.0,
      "text": "and it provides us with information to identify what to focus on next"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 365609.0,
      "end_time": 367929.0,
      "text": "when we go back to the learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 367929.0,
      "end_time": 369649.0,
      "text": "So the way to high performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 369649.0,
      "end_time": 373369.0,
      "text": "is to alternate between the learning zone and the performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 373369.0,
      "end_time": 375929.0,
      "text": "purposefully building our skills in the learning zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 375929.0,
      "end_time": 379369.0,
      "text": "then applying those skills in the performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 379369.0,
      "end_time": 381409.0,
      "text": "When Beyoncé is on tour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 381409.0,
      "end_time": 384609.0,
      "text": "during the concert, she&#39;s in her performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 384609.0,
      "end_time": 387129.0,
      "text": "but every night when she gets back to the hotel room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 387129.0,
      "end_time": 389369.0,
      "text": "she goes right back into her learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 389369.0,
      "end_time": 392169.0,
      "text": "She watches a video of the show that just ended."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 392169.0,
      "end_time": 394329.0,
      "text": "She identifies opportunities for improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 394329.0,
      "end_time": 396969.0,
      "text": "for herself, her dancers and her camera staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 396969.0,
      "end_time": 398249.0,
      "text": "And the next morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 398249.0,
      "end_time": 401329.0,
      "text": "everyone receives pages of notes with what to adjust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 401329.0,
      "end_time": 405329.0,
      "text": "which they then work on during the day before the next performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 405329.0,
      "end_time": 406569.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a spiral"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406569.0,
      "end_time": 408169.0,
      "text": "to ever-increasing capabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 408169.0,
      "end_time": 411809.0,
      "text": "but we need to know when we seek to learn, and when we seek to perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 411809.0,
      "end_time": 413889.0,
      "text": "and while we want to spend time doing both,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 413889.0,
      "end_time": 416009.0,
      "text": "the more time we spend in the learning zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 416009.0,
      "end_time": 418169.0,
      "text": "the more we&#39;ll improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 418169.0,
      "end_time": 421849.0,
      "text": "So how can we spend more time in the learning zone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 421849.0,
      "end_time": 425049.0,
      "text": "First, we must believe and understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 425049.0,
      "end_time": 426409.0,
      "text": "that we can improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 426409.0,
      "end_time": 428649.0,
      "text": "what we call a growth mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 428649.0,
      "end_time": 431929.0,
      "text": "Second, we must want to improve at that particular skill."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 431929.0,
      "end_time": 433889.0,
      "text": "There has to be a purpose we care about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 433889.0,
      "end_time": 436169.0,
      "text": "because it takes time and effort."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 436169.0,
      "end_time": 439209.0,
      "text": "Third, we must have an idea about how to improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 439209.0,
      "end_time": 440929.0,
      "text": "what we can do to improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 440929.0,
      "end_time": 443529.0,
      "text": "not how I used to practice the guitar as a teenager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 443529.0,
      "end_time": 445649.0,
      "text": "performing songs over and over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 445649.0,
      "end_time": 447769.0,
      "text": "but doing deliberate practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 447769.0,
      "end_time": 451969.0,
      "text": "And fourth, we must be in a low-stakes situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 451969.0,
      "end_time": 454209.0,
      "text": "because if mistakes are to be expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 454209.0,
      "end_time": 457249.0,
      "text": "then the consequence of making them must not be catastrophic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 457249.0,
      "end_time": 459049.0,
      "text": "or even very significant."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 459049.0,
      "end_time": 462769.0,
      "text": "A tightrope walker doesn&#39;t practice new tricks without a net underneath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 462769.0,
      "end_time": 465409.0,
      "text": "and an athlete wouldn&#39;t set out to first try a new move"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 465409.0,
      "end_time": 467929.0,
      "text": "during a championship match."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 467929.0,
      "end_time": 469609.0,
      "text": "One reason that in our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 469609.0,
      "end_time": 472089.0,
      "text": "we spend so much time in the performance zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 472089.0,
      "end_time": 477009.0,
      "text": "is that our environments often are, unnecessarily, high stakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 477009.0,
      "end_time": 479249.0,
      "text": "We create social risks for one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 479249.0,
      "end_time": 482129.0,
      "text": "even in schools which are supposed to be all about learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 482129.0,
      "end_time": 484289.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m not talking about standardized tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 484289.0,
      "end_time": 486529.0,
      "text": "I mean that every minute of every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 486529.0,
      "end_time": 489249.0,
      "text": "many students in elementary schools through colleges"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 489249.0,
      "end_time": 492689.0,
      "text": "feel that if they make a mistake, others will think less of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 492689.0,
      "end_time": 494649.0,
      "text": "No wonder they&#39;re always stressed out"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 494649.0,
      "end_time": 497569.0,
      "text": "and not taking the risks necessary for learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 497569.0,
      "end_time": 499849.0,
      "text": "But they learn that mistakes are undesirable"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 499849.0,
      "end_time": 501129.0,
      "text": "inadvertently"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 501129.0,
      "end_time": 504649.0,
      "text": "when teachers or parents are eager to hear just correct answers"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 504649.0,
      "end_time": 507329.0,
      "text": "and reject mistakes rather than welcome and examine them"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 507329.0,
      "end_time": 508609.0,
      "text": "to learn from them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 508609.0,
      "end_time": 510369.0,
      "text": "or when we look for narrow responses"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 510369.0,
      "end_time": 512609.0,
      "text": "rather than encourage more exploratory thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 512609.00000000006,
      "end_time": 513969.00000000006,
      "text": "that we can all learn from."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 513969.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517089.00000000006,
      "text": "When all homework or student work has a number or a letter on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 517089.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518849.00000000006,
      "text": "and counts towards a final grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 518849.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522449.00000000006,
      "text": "rather than being used for practice, mistakes, feedback and revision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 522448.99999999994,
      "end_time": 527049.0,
      "text": "we send the message that school is a performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 527049.0,
      "end_time": 529129.0,
      "text": "The same is true in our workplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 529129.0,
      "end_time": 533169.0,
      "text": "In the companies I consult with, I often see flawless execution cultures"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 533169.0,
      "end_time": 535769.0,
      "text": "which leaders foster to encourage great work."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 535769.0,
      "end_time": 538329.0,
      "text": "But that leads employees to stay within what they know"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 538329.0,
      "end_time": 539609.0,
      "text": "and not try new things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 539609.0,
      "end_time": 541969.0,
      "text": "so companies struggle to innovate and improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 541969.0,
      "end_time": 544769.0,
      "text": "and they fall behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 544769.0,
      "end_time": 547089.0,
      "text": "We can create more spaces for growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 547089.0,
      "end_time": 549169.0,
      "text": "by starting conversations with one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 549169.0,
      "end_time": 552049.0,
      "text": "about when we want to be in each zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 552049.0,
      "end_time": 554769.0,
      "text": "What do we want to get better at and how?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 554769.0,
      "end_time": 558489.0,
      "text": "And when do we want to execute and minimize mistakes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 558489.0,
      "end_time": 561529.0,
      "text": "That way, we gain clarity about what success is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 561529.0,
      "end_time": 564809.0,
      "text": "when, and how to best support one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 564809.0,
      "end_time": 567929.0,
      "text": "But what if we find ourselves in a chronic high-stakes setting"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 567929.0,
      "end_time": 571529.0,
      "text": "and we feel we can&#39;t start those conversations yet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 571529.0,
      "end_time": 574649.0,
      "text": "Then here are three things that we can still do as individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 574649.0,
      "end_time": 579449.0,
      "text": "First, we can create low-stakes islands in an otherwise high-stakes sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 579449.0,
      "end_time": 582209.0,
      "text": "These are spaces where mistakes have little consequence."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 582209.0,
      "end_time": 585689.0,
      "text": "For example, we might find a mentor or a trusted colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 585689.0,
      "end_time": 588889.0,
      "text": "with whom we can exchange ideas or have vulnerable conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 588889.0,
      "end_time": 590289.0,
      "text": "or even role-play."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 590289.0,
      "end_time": 593929.0,
      "text": "Or we can ask for feedback-oriented meetings as projects progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 593929.0,
      "end_time": 598089.0,
      "text": "Or we can set aside time to read or watch videos or take online courses."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 598089.0,
      "end_time": 600169.0,
      "text": "Those are just some examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 600169.0,
      "end_time": 604369.0,
      "text": "Second, we can execute and perform as we&#39;re expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 604369.0,
      "end_time": 606969.0,
      "text": "but then reflect on what we could do better next time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 606969.0,
      "end_time": 608249.0,
      "text": "like Beyoncé does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 608249.0,
      "end_time": 610409.0,
      "text": "and we can observe and emulate experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 610409.0,
      "end_time": 614689.0,
      "text": "The observation, reflection and adjustment is a learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 614689.0,
      "end_time": 617569.0,
      "text": "And finally, we can lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 617569.0,
      "end_time": 621169.0,
      "text": "and lower the stakes for others by sharing what we want to get better at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 621169.0,
      "end_time": 623689.0,
      "text": "by asking questions about what we don&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 623689.0,
      "end_time": 626209.0,
      "text": "by soliciting feedback and by sharing our mistakes"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 626209.0,
      "end_time": 627849.0,
      "text": "and what we&#39;ve learned from them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 627849.0,
      "end_time": 630569.0,
      "text": "so that others can feel safe to do the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 630569.0,
      "end_time": 635689.0,
      "text": "Real confidence is about modeling ongoing learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 635689.0,
      "end_time": 640169.0,
      "text": "What if, instead of spending our lives doing, doing, doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 640169.0,
      "end_time": 642289.0,
      "text": "performing, performing, performing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 642289.0,
      "end_time": 645449.0,
      "text": "we spent more time exploring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 645449.0,
      "end_time": 646889.0,
      "text": "asking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 646889.0,
      "end_time": 648209.0,
      "text": "listening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 648209.0,
      "end_time": 651329.0,
      "text": "experimenting, reflecting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 651329.0,
      "end_time": 655129.0,
      "text": "striving and becoming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 655129.0,
      "end_time": 657969.0,
      "text": "What if we each always had something"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 657969.0,
      "end_time": 660569.0,
      "text": "we were working to improve?"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 660569.0,
      "end_time": 663009.0,
      "text": "What if we created more low-stakes islands"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 663009.0,
      "end_time": 664649.0,
      "text": "and waters?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 664649.0,
      "end_time": 667129.0,
      "text": "And what if we got clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 667129.0,
      "end_time": 669529.0,
      "text": "within ourselves and with our teammates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 669529.0,
      "end_time": 673089.0,
      "text": "about when we seek to learn and when we seek to perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 673089.0,
      "end_time": 676169.0,
      "text": "so that our efforts can become more consequential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 676169.0,
      "end_time": 678849.0,
      "text": "our improvement never-ending"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 678849.0,
      "end_time": 681809.0,
      "text": "and our best even better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 681809.0,
      "end_time": 683047.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 683047.0,
      "end_time": 693047.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}